OL,3,CJersey's Health Minister 'cautiously
OL,4,Coptimistic' about new hospital plans
OL,6,FJersey's Health Minister says he is
OL,7,F"cautiously optimistic" that plans for
OL,8,Fthe island's new acute hospital will
OL,9,Fbe a success.
OL,11,FDeputy Tom Binet told ITV News that he
OL,12,Fis confident about the prospects for
OL,13,FOverdale Hospital if the planning
OL,14,Fapplication is passed in the States.
OL,16,FHe said: "With the track record we've
OL,17,Fgot, I've got to be cautious here -
OL,18,Fbut I'm cautiously optimistic.
