OL,3,CJersey's Health Minister 'cautiously
OL,4,Coptimistic' about new hospital plans
OL,6,F"It's a sensible plan. It still sits
OL,7,Fwithin its original budget and it
OL,8,Fseems to have been well received by
OL,9,Fall concerned."
OL,11,FPreparation work to clear the old
OL,12,FOverdale site at Westmount began in
OL,13,FSeptember 2023 with Jersey's Health
OL,14,FDepartment planning for Overdale
OL,15,FHospital to become home to the
OL,16,Fisland's acute healthcare services by
OL,17,F2028.
OL,19,FDeputy Binet explained why he believes
OL,20,Fthe new Overdale site would upgrade
OL,21,Fthe island's current facilities.
