OL,3,CJersey's Health Minister 'cautiously
OL,4,Coptimistic' about new hospital plans
OL,6,FHe said: "In relative terms, it's
OL,7,Fcheaper. The numbers might be similar.
OL,8,FThey wouldn't be similar if we hadn't
OL,9,Fhad the inflation that we've had.
OL,11,F"The structure is actually quite a lot
OL,12,Fsmaller. It's lower and it's more
OL,13,Fspread, it makes better use of the
OL,14,Fsite. So less environmental impact."
OL,16,FThe project is estimated to cost #710
OL,17,Fmillion pounds.
