OL,3,CJersey's Health Minister 'cautiously
OL,4,Coptimistic' about new hospital plans
OL,6,FWhen asked about the project's value
OL,7,Ffor money, Deputy Binet said: "They
OL,8,Fget a state-of-the-art acute hospital
OL,9,Ffor the next 60 years."
OL,11,FHe added: "When you look at the
OL,12,Fsituation that people are working in
OL,13,Fat the minute, that's not ideal and
OL,14,Fthat's not sustainable in the long
OL,15,Fterm."
